<item>
            <title>[LU-14533] Interop: sanity-pfl test 0d fails with  &apos;creating /mnt/lustre/d0d.sanity-pfl/f0d.sanity-pfl-1 failed&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14533</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-pfl test_0d started failing on 2021-02-28 for interop testing for Lustre clients 2.14.50.115 and Lustre servers 2.13.0; &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6fbbf6b5-b0ce-4446-a124-b9501cc401af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/6fbbf6b5-b0ce-4446-a124-b9501cc401af&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In the suite_log, we see&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity-pfl test 0d: Verify comp end and stripe size =============================================== 01:08:21 (1615770501)
lfs setstripe: cannot create composite file &apos;/mnt/lustre/d0d.sanity-pfl/f0d.sanity-pfl-1&apos;: Invalid argument
 sanity-pfl test_0d: @@@@@@ FAIL: creating /mnt/lustre/d0d.sanity-pfl/f0d.sanity-pfl-1 failed 
  Trace dump:
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh:5991:error()
  = /usr/lib64/lustre/tests/sanity-pfl.sh:113:test_0d()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-pfl test 0d was added to Lustre 2.14.50 with patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/41239&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/41239&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14180&quot; title=&quot;&amp;quot;lfs setstripe -E&amp;quot; doesn&amp;#39;t validate component end&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-14180&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-14180&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; utils: verify setstripe comp_end is valid)and should be skipped for Lustre server &amp;lt; 2.14.51.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
